{"tid":470085,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"偷食男艾沙維靠誠意挽婚姻","createTime":"2017-11-16T03:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T04:18:48.000Z","uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d54fddb2803416a65865d9a5bda1cd7d41502633","tid":470085,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=HEhLnMtwE8kNTIt9u6ef2AHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=b6bf284e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】上月，前阿仙奴前鋒艾沙維因為偷食而面臨離婚，不過其太太Alisa最近表示會給予沙皇多一次機會。<br />\n<br />\n正於哈薩克超聯球隊卡拉特效力的艾沙維（Andrey Arshavin），早前被第2任太太Alisa發現偷食，結果後者決定離婚，結束約1年的婚姻。不過，經過艾沙維不停挽救，Alisa被他的誠意打動，決定回心轉意。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「以艾沙維的名氣，他的舉動很震撼我。我們有一個家庭，在一起的感覺亦很好，我希望亦準備好給予他多一次機會。」<br />\n<br />\n曾效力阿仙奴的艾沙維跟Alisa今次破鏡重圓，相信最大得益者是他們9個月大的女兒，不用受家庭破碎之苦。Alisa是艾沙維的第2任妻子，這名36歲前俄羅斯國腳於2013年跟第1任太太Julia結束9年婚姻，兩人育有3名子女。"},{"pid":"72e270afcf43094fbe76027b02b23d8e4cd0129a","tid":470085,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"小學雞生咁多件既"},{"pid":"7e848b22842de167b042db61fec110808f8858fe","tid":470085,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:17:16.000Z","msg":"艾沙拉維？"},{"pid":"4ed170fe2ad0c9f67b9333a18bee52913c83e66a","tid":470085,"uid":76063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:20:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.dni.ru/binaries/v2_articlephotoauto/806215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.dni.ru%2Fbinaries%2Fv2_articlephotoauto%2F806215.jpg&h=157de583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n似哥哥多過似老豆"},{"pid":"32b9b07736bac0502dca87a639d3d4ed81b2b3cf","tid":470085,"uid":15862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.dni.ru/binaries/v2_articlephotoauto/806215.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fim